title: Whiting Furnished/Utilities Paid
posting_body: ['Furnished/Utilities paid!', 'Two story apartment in 100 Yr old house!', 'Available July 1, 2022!', 'Flexible floor plan!', 'Lease preferred.', 'Furnished/Flexible 1-2 bedroom Very comfortable.', "Great starter apartment for someone who doesn't have a lot of furniture!", 'This apartment has been used by students, BP contractors, and families alike over the years.', 'It has utilities, water, internet and cable included!', 'Very close to Chicago (17 miles from downtown)', 'Private entrance.', 'Easy street parking available.', 'Corner lot.', 'Very Peaceful!', 'Furnished.', '(TV, nice big fridge, 100 yr old house, charming!', 'private entrance, nice big backyard, grill)', 'Clean.', 'LOTS of closet space.', 'Close to Chicago Skyway and two blocks from the beach.', 'Parks, bike trails, etc.', 'Whiting!', 'Lots of festivals, stuff to do.', 'This 2 story apartment has been used as both 1 or 2 bedroom - it is flexible and somewhat large - with upstairs finished attic/bedroom and lots of closet space.', 'Lots of trees.', 'Quiet and Shady.', 'There is a staircase to access the apartment and there is also a staircase inside the apartment.', 'please no smoking - no pets.', 'One month deposit and credit check.', 'Email if interested.', 'Thank you!']
